00:12:10.500 --> 00:12:12.164
We talked about this before.

00:12:12.164 --> 00:12:13.830
If I think about the
input of the system

00:12:13.830 --> 00:12:18.232
being the position of
the top of the spring,

00:12:18.232 --> 00:12:20.190
and if I think about the
response of the system

00:12:20.190 --> 00:12:25.050
being the position
of the mass, then I

00:12:25.050 --> 00:12:29.230
can characterize that system as
a linear time invariant system.

00:12:29.230 --> 00:12:31.830
And I can think about how
does the amplitude change

00:12:31.830 --> 00:12:36.160
and how does the phase change,
as a function of frequency

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:39.060
of the sinusoid.

00:12:39.060 --> 00:12:40.860
OK, this is just like
the music example,

00:12:40.860 --> 00:12:42.420
